<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,717,2026]" pageId="4" pageNumber="56">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,355,1117,1143]" pageId="4" pageNumber="56">Recognition.</emphasis>
This genus and species may be distinguished from other North American empidoids by its yellow colour, bare eyes, lack of distinct acrostichals and the postpedicel with dense grey pubescence.
</paragraph>
